OL,3,CFamilies of Chinook crash victims
OL,4,Cpress on with legal action against MoD
OL,6,FThe families of those killed in the
OL,7,F1994 Chinook helicopter crash have
OL,8,Fsaid they will press on with seeking a
OL,9,Fjudicial review after the Ministry of
OL,10,FDefence (MoD) dismissed their demands
OL,11,Ffor a judge-led public inquiry.
OL,13,FRAF Chinook ZD576 was carrying 25
OL,14,FBritish intelligence personnel from
OL,15,FRAF Aldergrove in Northern Ireland to
OL,16,Fa conference at Fort George near
OL,17,FInverness when it crashed in foggy
OL,18,Fweather on June 2 1994 on the Mull of
OL,19,FKintyre.
