OL,6,FAll 25 passengers ` made up of
OL,7,Fpersonnel from MI5, the Royal Ulster
OL,8,FConstabulary and the British Army `
OL,9,Fwere killed, along with the
OL,10,Fhelicopter's four crew members.
OL,12,FThe families launched legal action in
OL,13,Fa "letter before action" to the UK
OL,14,FGovernment sent earlier this month on
OL,15,Fthe 31st anniversary of the crash.
