OL,3,CFamilies of Chinook crash victims
OL,4,Cpress on with legal action against MoD
OL,6,FThey said they will now pursue a
OL,7,Fjudicial review after the MoD
OL,8,Fresponded and rejected their demands
OL,9,Ffor a public inquiry into the
OL,10,Fcircumstances surrounding the crash,
OL,11,Fand for access to files which have
OL,12,Fbeen sealed for 100 years.
OL,14,FNicola Rawcliffe, whose brother Major
OL,15,FChristopher Dockerty was killed in the
OL,16,Fcrash aged 33, said: "I am furious and
OL,17,Fdisgusted with the MoD's decision to
OL,18,Fsummarily dismiss our claim.
