OL,3,CFamilies of Chinook crash victims
OL,4,Cpress on with legal action against MoD
OL,6,FThe MoD said the crash was a "tragic
OL,7,Faccident" and while its sympathies
OL,8,Fremain with the families and friends
OL,9,Fof the victims, there have been
OL,10,Fseveral investigations and inquiries
OL,11,Fand it believes it is unlikely another
OL,12,Fwould reach any new conclusions.
OL,14,FAndy Tobias, who was eight when his
OL,15,Ffather Lieutenant Colonel John Tobias,
OL,16,F41, was killed, said: "My childhood
OL,17,Fwas stolen from me because someone
OL,18,Fdecided my dad and his colleagues
OL,19,Fshould be put on a helicopter that was
OL,20,Fnot fit for purpose.
