OL,6,FSolicitor Mark Stephens, from law firm
OL,7,FHoward Kennedy, said: "This decision
OL,8,Fby the MoD to dismiss our claim is an
OL,9,Funforgivable betrayal of service
OL,10,Fpeople who gave their lives for their
OL,11,Fcountry and an undisguised slap in the
OL,12,Fface for their long-suffering and
OL,13,Fbereaved families.
OL,15,F"So much for the Government's so-
OL,16,Fcalled commitment to duty of candour.
OL,18,F"We will now seek a judicial review
OL,19,Finto the Ministry of Defence's
OL,20,Fdecision to deny the families truth,
OL,21,Ftransparency and justice."
