OL,6,FAn MoD spokesperson said: "The Mull of
OL,7,FKintyre crash was a tragic accident,
OL,8,Fand our thoughts and sympathies remain
OL,9,Fwith the families, friends and
OL,10,Fcolleagues of all those who died.
OL,12,F"We understand that the lack of
OL,13,Fcertainty about the cause of the crash
OL,14,Fhas added to the distress of the
OL,15,Ffamilies.
OL,17,F"We provided a detailed and considered
OL,18,Fresponse to the pre-action protocol
OL,19,Fletter stating the reasons why we
OL,20,Fcannot accept the demand for
OL,21,Festablishing a new public inquiry.
