OL,6,F"It's unlikely that a public inquiry
OL,7,Fwould identify any new evidence or
OL,8,Freach new conclusions on the basis of
OL,9,Fexisting evidence.
OL,11,F"The accident has already been the
OL,12,Fsubject of six inquiries and
OL,13,Finvestigations, including an
OL,14,Findependent judge-led review."
OL,16,FIt is understood the sealed documents
OL,17,Fcontain personal information relating
OL,18,Fto third party individuals and the
OL,19,Fearly release of this information
OL,20,Fwould breach those individuals' data
OL,21,Fprotection rights.
